headline: Should You Invest $1,000 in Verizon Today?
summary: Verizon's stock outperformed the S&P 500 this year.  The telecom company Verizon Communications (NYSE: VZ) enjoyed a solid first half of 2025, with its stock up nearly 9%, soundly beating the broader benchmark S&P 500 index, which is up 1%.  Verizon is already one of the major players in the mature wireless market.
